messages.message:
Good morning/evening/<insert arbitrary time window here>!

Heads-up that I'm making a change to the pre-merge which runs on every commit for every PR - *please let me know if you run into any issues with PR commits that fail on pr-merge for no good reason!*

(But please _*do*_ check that any pr-merge failures on your PR(s) are not actually the result of your own changes. :slightly_smiling_face:)
Details in this RelEng thread (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C035SLYCJ9X/p1706545915800999).
